metadata.name: Mother of Rice
metadata.description: Mother of Rice is a single edition NFT by the senior and internationally renowned Thai artist, Vasan Sitthiket. The NFT artwork has been rendered as a unique etching that celebrates Mother Earth as the provider of rice and abundance in this world. Vasan Sitthiket is one of Thailand's most prominent and respected artists, who works in a variety of media and often focuses on socio-political and environmental issues.
